              ],
              "free_text": [
                " CsI(Tl) crystal (Harshaw Chemical Comp.) of",
                "of 10x10x1.6 mm**3 or 10x10x0.25 mm**3 and FEU-176 (",
                "with photocathode diameter 15 mm.",
                "Both crystals had 5.5 microm Al mylar reflector on the",
                "front polish surface.",
